---
---
<!-- Berserk CLI Section -->
<section class="py-24 px-8 md:px-24 bg-surface-container-lowest border-t border-primary/10">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16">
  <div class="reveal md:w-1/3">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="h-8 w-2 bg-primary"></span>
      BERSERK CLI
    </h2>
    <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8 leading-relaxed">
      A curated package manager for offensive security tools. Install, update, and manage your entire toolkit from a single command.
    </p>
    <div class="space-y-5 mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg mt-0.5" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">terminal</span>
        <div>
          <div class="text-on-surface font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Multi-backend</div>
          <div class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Installs via Go, Cargo, pip, npm, gem, pacman, and GitHub releases.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg mt-0.5" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">category</span>
        <div>
          <div class="text-on-surface font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Profiles & Categories</div>
          <div class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Install entire toolkits by profile — AD attacks, web hacking, recon, and more.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg mt-0.5" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">deployed_code</span>
        <div>
          <div class="text-on-surface font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Docker Containers</div>
          <div class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Run pre-configured containers like Kali CLI and Tor Browser directly from the catalog.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a
      href="https://github.com/thehackersbrain/berserk"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="btn-outline inline-flex items-center gap-2 !px-6 !py-3 !text-xs"
    >
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">open_in_new</span>
      VIEW ON GITHUB
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="reveal reveal-delay-200 md:w-2/3 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-primary/30 relative">
    <div class="bg-surface-container-high px-4 py-2 flex items-center justify-between border-b border-primary/20">
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary"></div>
        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary/40"></div>
        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary/20"></div>
      </div>
      <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-primary font-bold">terminal — berserk</span>
    </div>
    <pre class="p-8 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto text-on-surface-variant m-0"><code><span class="text-primary font-bold">guts@berserkarch</span> ~ $ <span class="text-on-surface">berserk install --profile web-hacking</span>

<span class="text-primary">⠋</span> Installing profile <span class="text-on-surface font-bold">web-hacking</span> (12 tools)

<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">nuclei</span>        go install     <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">httpx</span>         go install     <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">ffuf</span>          go install     <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">sqlmap</span>        pipx           <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">feroxbuster</span>   cargo install  <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">katana</span>        go install     <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">subfinder</span>     go install     <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">naabu</span>         go install     <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">dnsx</span>          go install     <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">gau</span>           go install     <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">arjun</span>         pipx           <span class="text-primary">latest</span>
<span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span class="text-on-surface">waybackurls</span>   go install     <span class="text-primary">latest</span>

<span class="text-on-surface font-bold">12/12 tools installed successfully.</span>

<span class="text-primary font-bold">guts@berserkarch</span> ~ $ <span class="animate-pulse text-primary font-bold">_</span></code></pre>
  </div>
</div>
</section>
